Dialogue: 100,0:00:03.58,0:00:06.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道我妈妈做了些非常不好的事\N{\rENG}I know my mom did something really bad.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:06.60,0:00:09.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}无论母星准备如何惩治我\N{\rENG}Whatever Homeworld has in store for me...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:09.56,0:00:10.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}放马来吧\N{\rENG}I'm ready!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.47,0:00:15.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我说 放马来吧\N{\rENG}I said, I'm ready!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.98,0:00:18.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是我 玫瑰石英\N{\rENG}It's me -- Rose Quartz!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.74,0:00:19.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喂\N{\rENG}Hello?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.18,0:00:21.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有人吗\N{\rENG}Anybody?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.30,0:00:23.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯 你在哪\N{\rENG}Lars, are you there?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.18,0:00:25.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是惩罚吗\N{\rENG}Is this the punishment?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:26.18,0:00:27.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拜托\N{\rENG}Come on!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道惩罚肯定比这要重\N{\rENG}I know it's going to be worse than this!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.58,0:00:31.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以无论你们接下来要做什么\N{\rENG}So whatever you're gonna do...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:31.82,0:00:33.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拜托 赶紧动手吧\N{\rENG}would you just do it already?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.24,0:00:35.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}简直荒唐透顶\N{\rENG}This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对法庭效忠了4000年之久\N{\rENG}4,000 years of loyal service to the court,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.02,0:00:39.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}最后居然摊上这种倒霉事\N{\rENG}and this is what I get?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.36,0:00:41.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 我简直是这个星系最倒霉的锆石了\N{\rENG}Oh, I'm the unluckiest zircon in the galaxy!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.64,0:00:44.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等下 你是...\N{\rENG}Wait, are you...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.83,0:00:46.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰石英?\N{\rENG}Rose Quartz?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.68,0:00:47.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.58,0:00:49.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}骗人吧\N{\rENG}Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一言难尽\N{\rENG}It's a long story.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.77,0:00:53.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那我可没空听你解释\N{\rENG}Then I don't have time for it.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.24,0:00:56.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 我们就只有这片刻时间来准备你的案件\N{\rENG}Ugh! We only have this brief moment to prepare your case.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.54,0:00:57.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}案件\N{\rENG}Case?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.54,0:00:59.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃啊 我到底在干嘛\N{\rENG}Ugh! Who am I kidding?!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.25,0:01:00.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这毫无意义\N{\rENG}This is pointless!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.38,0:01:02.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们都听说关于粉钻之死的那些流言了\N{\rENG}We've all heard the rumors about the demise
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.38,0:01:05.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是我实在不能相信这些文件\N{\rENG}of Pink Diamond, but I can't believe these files!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.05,0:01:07.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}被一个--她自己的士兵所杀--哈\N{\rENG}Shattered by one - of her own soldiers -- ha!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.52,0:01:09.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还是当着她整班随从的面\N{\rENG}In front of her entire entourage!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.92,0:01:11.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有看看你现在的样子\N{\rENG}And look at you now!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.39,0:01:13.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这滑稽的伪装只会让你\N{\rENG}That ridiculous disguise is only going to make you
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.24,0:01:14.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看起来更有罪\N{\rENG}look more guilty!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.73,0:01:16.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没关系 因为我就是有罪\N{\rENG}That's fine, because I am!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别这么说\N{\rENG}Well, don't say that --
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.23,0:01:20.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}尤其是等会儿你到了外面的时候\N{\rENG}especially not when you're out there!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.07,0:01:22.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}外面是哪? 到底会发生什么\N{\rENG}Out where?! - What's going to happen!?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.30,0:01:25.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你认为会发生什么?! 玫瑰石英!\N{\rENG}What did you think was going to happen, Rose Quartz?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.87,0:01:31.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一旦那扇门一打开 你就要被审判了!\N{\rENG}As soon as that door opens, you're going on trial!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.11,0:01:32.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢\N{\rENG}Oh.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.39,0:01:42.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为一个叛徒辩护?\N{\rENG}Defending a rebel?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.96,0:01:45.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是不是算 叛星罪了\N{\rENG}Isn't that...treason?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.89,0:01:47.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是被分配干这个的\N{\rENG}I was assigned to this!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.92,0:01:54.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}全体起立 向光辉的黄钻石致敬\N{\rENG}All rise for the luminous Yellow Diamond!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.30,0:01:57.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}向辉煌的蓝钻石致意\N{\rENG}And the lustrous Blue Diamond.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.04,0:02:09.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}被告人呢\N{\rENG}Where is the accused?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.82,0:02:12.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那就是玫瑰石英吗\N{\rENG}Is that Rose Quartz?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看她现在那丑不忍睹的形态\N{\rENG}Look at this hideous form she's taken.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.95,0:02:16.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别管审判了\N{\rENG}Forget the trial.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.32,0:02:19.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}光是维持这种形态就应该判死罪了\N{\rENG}We should shatter her just for looking like that.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.29,0:02:22.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不行 我要听她自己的申诉\N{\rENG}No! I want to hear her make her case.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.53,0:02:26.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想要知道她认为我们会怎么处置她\N{\rENG}I want to know what she thinks we're going to do with her,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.03,0:02:29.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为我想做的比那更残酷\N{\rENG}because I want to do something worse.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.14,0:02:34.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}行 那就让我们开始吧\N{\rENG}Fine! Let's just get on with it, shall we?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.68,0:02:43.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的钻石 我杰出的 豪富的 光芒四射的 闪烁的--\N{\rENG}My Diamond. My brilliant, opulent, radiant, glimmering --
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.30,0:02:46.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只要说"我的钻石"就足够了 不然我们一辈子都完成不了\N{\rENG}"My Diamond" will suffice, or we'll never get through this.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.99,0:02:48.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然 我的钻石\N{\rENG}Of course, My Diamond.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.52,0:02:53.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰石英犯下如此史无前例的罪\N{\rENG}Rose Quartz committed a crime so unprecedented
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.08,0:02:56.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}使人不得不提出疑问--为什么\N{\rENG}that one can't help but wonder -- why?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呈上"证物"A\N{\rENG}Exhibit "A."
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯\N{\rENG}Lars!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 到底发生了什么\N{\rENG}Steven! What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.56,0:03:04.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们在哪\N{\rENG}Where are we?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那些巨大的女士们又是谁\N{\rENG}Who are those huge, giant ladies?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}正如我们从这个样品中可以看出的\N{\rENG}As we can see from this specimen...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}毫无疑问 人类是喧嚣又丑陋的生物\N{\rENG}...humans are loud, absolutely hideous creatures
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它们的存在毫无意义\N{\rENG}that serve no purpose whatsoever.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.38,0:03:17.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}又有什么样的宝石人会为了人类而背叛自己的同类呢\N{\rENG}What sort of gem would turn on her own kind for this?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.25,0:03:20.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我来告诉你们--就是那样的\N{\rENG}I'll tell you what kind -- that kind.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.39,0:03:23.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}放他走 他与案件毫无联系\N{\rENG}Just let him go! He's got nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.52,0:03:26.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看看--就是这样的冲动 这样的暴怒--\N{\rENG}There it is -- the passion, the fury --
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.84,0:03:30.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}驱使残忍的玫瑰石英去\N{\rENG}that caused the diabolical Rose Quartz to...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.72,0:03:33.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}粉碎自己的钻石\N{\rENG}shatter her own diamond!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道你们在想什么\N{\rENG}But I know what you're thinking...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.54,0:03:40.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"这玩意儿可不像玫瑰石英啊"\N{\rENG}"This thing doesn't look like a Rose Quartz."
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.04,0:03:43.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因此 我特地叫来了一位目击证石\N{\rENG}And for that, I would like to call an eyewitness!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.78,0:03:49.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 眼宝\N{\rENG}Oh, Eyeball!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别给我瞎起名 你这战犯\N{\rENG}Do not address me, war criminal!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只是很高兴你没事\N{\rENG}I'm just glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是听她亲口说的 她说\N{\rENG}I heard it straight from her. She said...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.82,0:04:01.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"我就是那个伟大的玫瑰石英"\N{\rENG}"I'm the mighty Rose Quartz.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.06,0:04:04.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"我有她的盾牌啊啥的"\N{\rENG}I've got her shield and everything."
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.40,0:04:08.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后她把我扔进了太空\N{\rENG}And then she threw me into space!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.40,0:04:11.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是在试着救你 我治愈了你的宝石\N{\rENG}I tried to help you! I healed your gem!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以说除了邪恶的\N{\rENG}And who else has the ability
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.41,0:04:16.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰石英 还有谁有\N{\rENG}to heal gems other than the villainous...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.91,0:04:19.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}治愈宝石的能力\N{\rENG}Rose Quartz?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以那么我们证实了\N{\rENG}And there you have it!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.71,0:04:23.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是玫瑰石英干的 而那就是玫瑰石英\N{\rENG}Rose Quartz did it, and that's Rose Quartz.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.08,0:04:24.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我说完了\N{\rENG}I rest my case.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 她可真棒\N{\rENG}Oh, she's good.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.42,0:04:32.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘛 我相信了 行刑吧\N{\rENG}Well, I'm convinced! Time to execute!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.26,0:04:36.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还没完呢 辩护律师还得发言\N{\rENG}Not yet. The defense still has to speak.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.16,0:04:37.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对啊 啊 呃\N{\rENG}Right! Well, uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.50,0:04:41.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在我开始 我的 呃 深思熟虑的辩护之前\N{\rENG}Before I start, my very, uh, thought-out defense,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.07,0:04:42.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想要提醒法庭的各位\N{\rENG}I'd like to remind the court
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰石英确实自首了\N{\rENG}that Rose Quartz did turn herself in.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.77,0:04:48.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}法庭记得 法庭也不关心\N{\rENG}The Court remembers, and the Court does not care.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.94,0:04:52.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 当然 呃 无-无辜\N{\rENG}Uh, of course. Uh, in-- innocent!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 "无辜"这个词可以解释为\N{\rENG}Uh, the word "innocent" can mean,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 很多东西\N{\rENG}oh, many different things.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.68,0:04:57.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是我干的\N{\rENG}I did it!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什-- 啥 啥 停下\N{\rENG}Wha-- What, what! Stop!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.19,0:05:04.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想听她要说的内容\N{\rENG}I want to hear what she has to say.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}带我们逃出这里啊 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Get us out of here, Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃\N{\rENG}Uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为记录需要 请报上你的姓名\N{\rENG}State your name for the record, please!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我 呃\N{\rENG}I, um...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.37,0:05:20.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是玫瑰石英…我有罪\N{\rENG}I am Rose Quartz... and I'm guilty.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等下 不 别这么说啊\N{\rENG}Wait! No, don't say that!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.45,0:05:28.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们声称我做的那些事 都是真的\N{\rENG}Everything you guys said I did, I did.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.31,0:05:31.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}全部是我自己干的 我非常抱歉\N{\rENG}And I did it by myself. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会接受你们给我的任何惩罚\N{\rENG}I'll accept any punishment you want to give me.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.62,0:05:38.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只要你们放他走 不要再打地球的主意\N{\rENG}Just let him go! And leave the Earth alone.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.12,0:05:41.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈 听上去是个很标准的供认\N{\rENG}Ha! Sounds like a solid confession to me!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.29,0:05:44.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是怎样的 你是怎样做的\N{\rENG}How? How did you do it?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.63,0:05:49.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是怎样粉碎粉钻的\N{\rENG}How did you shatter Pink Diamond?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 嗯\N{\rENG}Um, well...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.64,0:05:55.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是在地球上 粉钻的轿子前做的\N{\rENG}I did it on Earth in front of Pink Diamond's palanquin.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.34,0:05:57.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我大概是"住手" 这样\N{\rENG}I was probably like "Stop!"
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后她说"我就不"\N{\rENG}And she was all like, "No!"
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.18,0:06:02.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以我们就打了起来--我想应该是\N{\rENG}So we fought -- I think.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.58,0:06:05.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后她也许就开了几个大\N{\rENG}And she probably did some cool moves.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可能也放了几个炫酷的招\N{\rENG}I probably did some cool stuff, too,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}飞踢啊什么的\N{\rENG}some jump kicks and stuff.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.16,0:06:12.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我应该是深深犹豫着\N{\rENG}But I was most likely deeply conflicted
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.16,0:06:13.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}要不要下杀手\N{\rENG}about deciding to shatter her.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.99,0:06:15.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}绝对是在一边痛哭着的\N{\rENG}Definitely crying.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可能是拿断裂极限干的\N{\rENG}I probably had to use the Breaking Point to do it.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是一把剑\N{\rENG}It was a sword!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.22,0:06:30.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你…是用一把剑…\N{\rENG}You...shattered her...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}粉碎她的\N{\rENG}with a sword!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你的口供已经够了\N{\rENG}That's quite enough testimony from you!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们需要短暂的中场休息\N{\rENG}We shall take a short recess.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在那都在胡说些什么\N{\rENG}What are you saying in there?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.09,0:06:42.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"也许"这个 "大概"那个\N{\rENG}"Maybe" this, "probably" that!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 你说"大概"是什么意思?!\N{\rENG}Oh, what do you mean probably?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听着 我只是\N{\rENG}Look, I just...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.36,0:06:48.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}实际上我不知道是怎么做的 好吗\N{\rENG}I don't actually know how it happened, okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不知道\N{\rENG}You don't know?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我\N{\rENG}I...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.03,0:06:53.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要挑战我的极限\N{\rENG}Don't tumble my rocks!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在我俩都是一根线上的蚂蚱\N{\rENG}Both our gems are on the line!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}到底是不是你干的\N{\rENG}Did you do this or not?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.07,0:06:59.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是我干的\N{\rENG}It was me, all right!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰干了 然后我拥有她的宝石\N{\rENG}Rose Quartz did it, and I've got her gem,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.74,0:07:04.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以我就得对此负责\N{\rENG}so I'm the one who's gotta pay for this!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.92,0:07:07.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不知道是怎么发生的\N{\rENG}You don't know how it happened.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.68,0:07:12.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我懂了 她们想要你解释怎么做的\N{\rENG}I get it. There's a reason they want you to explain
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是有原因的\N{\rENG}how you did it.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.29,0:07:18.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为这根本说不通!\N{\rENG}It's because it doesn't make sense!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰石英是有缺陷的 这点我同意\N{\rENG}Rose Quartz is flawed, I grant you.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.66,0:07:26.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个浅层的宝石出于一种被误导的\N{\rENG}A shallow strata gem who turned on her own kind
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对地球和这种生物的依恋\N{\rENG}out of a misguided attachment to a planet
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而背叛了自己的同类\N{\rENG}and creatures like these.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.67,0:07:32.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啥 什么\N{\rENG}What?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.10,0:07:35.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}正如钻石俯瞰地球那样明明白白\N{\rENG}It's indisputable that as the diamond overseeing Earth,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}粉钻是玫瑰石英的敌人\N{\rENG}Pink was Rose Quartz's enemy.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杀死粉钻对玫瑰石英来说有充分的动机\N{\rENG}Rose had everything to gain by shattering her.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.58,0:07:44.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但即使她想杀死粉钻\N{\rENG}But even though she may have wanted to shatter
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.12,0:07:46.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她做得到吗?\N{\rENG}Pink Diamond, could she?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.42,0:07:50.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蓝钻陛下 为了辩护的缘故\N{\rENG}Blue Diamond, for the purpose of this argument,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可以呈上您的轿子吗\N{\rENG}may I present your palanquin?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有必要吗\N{\rENG}Is this necessary?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.43,0:07:58.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}难道没有吗 请呈上\N{\rENG}Isn't it? Please, proceed.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.36,0:08:00.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 就像档案记录的\N{\rENG}Now, as the records show,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.63,0:08:04.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}粉钻就是在一个轿子前遇刺的\N{\rENG}Pink Diamond was shattered just outside a palanquin
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就像这个一样\N{\rENG}much like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}目击证石称 粉钻刚踏出轿子\N{\rENG}Witnesses said, Pink had stepped out
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.48,0:08:12.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就前行了几步\N{\rENG}and had taken only a few steps forward,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.18,0:08:14.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰石英就从正面袭击了她\N{\rENG}when Rose attacked her from the front.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢\N{\rENG}Oh!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.48,0:08:18.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但没人关注的是"怎么做的"\N{\rENG}The question no one seems to be asking is "how?"
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就在关注此事\N{\rENG}I've been asking that question.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.32,0:08:24.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}正-正-正-正如您所询问的 我的钻石\N{\rENG}A-a-a-and right you are to ask, My Diamond!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.72,0:08:27.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因-因为在粉钻遇刺的时候\N{\rENG}B-because, at the time that Pink was shattered,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰石英已经是几百年来\N{\rENG}Rose Quartz had been a recognized threat
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}公认的威胁了\N{\rENG}for several hundred years.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在粉钻的近身随从里没有玫瑰石英\N{\rENG}There were no Rose Quartz soldiers in her entourage,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}侍卫里也没有\N{\rENG}and none in her guard.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以 首先一个玫瑰石英\N{\rENG}So how did a Rose Quartz,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.91,0:08:43.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在没有任何理由接近粉钻的情况下\N{\rENG}with no business being anywhere near Pink Diamond,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是如何能够来到如此近身的地方呢\N{\rENG}get so close in the first place?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.51,0:08:48.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}粉钻她的随从呢\N{\rENG}Where were Pink Diamond's attendants?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她的玛瑙呢 她的蓝宝石呢\N{\rENG}Her Agates, her Sapphires?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.85,0:08:54.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有她的珍珠呢\N{\rENG}And where was her Pearl?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们就在她身边\N{\rENG}They were with her, of course.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们目击了全程\N{\rENG}They saw the whole thing!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.89,0:09:00.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但就没有一个看到玫瑰石英接近吗\N{\rENG}But none of them saw Rose Quartz approach?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.73,0:09:03.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她的蓝宝石不会预示玫瑰的到来吗\N{\rENG}Wouldn't her Sapphires have seen Rose Quartz coming?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.70,0:09:06.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她的玛瑙不会试图击退她吗\N{\rENG}Wouldn't her Agates have tried to fight her off?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这确实很可疑\N{\rENG}That is strange!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她一定是从她们之间溜过去了\N{\rENG}She must have slipped past them!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就算是这样\N{\rENG}Even if she did,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.04,0:09:15.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她的珍珠难道不会大声发出警告\N{\rENG}wouldn't her Pearl have cried out in alarm,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.11,0:09:19.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"千万小心 我的钻石"\N{\rENG}"Watch out, my Diamond!"
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.11,0:09:23.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 无论凶手是谁 她一定和粉钻关系亲密\N{\rENG}No, whoever did this was already close to Pink Diamond,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是一个粉钻的侍卫会让其接近\N{\rENG}someone her guards would allow to get near her,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是一个当要求停轿\N{\rENG}someone she would listen to
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}粉钻会听从并走出轿子\N{\rENG}when asked to stop her palanquin
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}的人\N{\rENG}and step outside,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.73,0:09:37.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还是一个能够在事后掩盖真相\N{\rENG}and someone with the authority to cover it up afterwards!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.36,0:09:39.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拥有无上权威的人\N{\rENG}Someone with supreme authority!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.43,0:09:43.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是一个你们中间的人\N{\rENG}Someone like one of you!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊 请无视最后那段陈述\N{\rENG}Uh, disregard that last statement!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可能有点入戏太深了\N{\rENG}I might have gotten carried away.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.24,0:09:54.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}结案了 对吧 我的钻石\N{\rENG}Case closed, right, My Diamond?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.92,0:09:59.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}黄 住手 你为什么要这么做\N{\rENG}Yellow, stop it! Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-好机会 我们快跑 -去哪\N{\rENG}This is our chance! We gotta go! - Where?!
